Package co.edu.unbosque.model.persistence

package co.edu.unbosque.model.persistence
In the MVC architecture, the Model represents the application's data, rules, and logic. Within this package, you'll find classes that serve as the heart of the application, managing data structures, algorithms, and interactions with databases.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Juan Pablo Urrego, Javier Meza Montero, Juan Esteban Quintero, Joann Alejandro Zamudio, Jeisson Nicolas Uyaban
